            <div class="charts-empty" data-chart-empty="size">No sizes found matching your search criteria.</div>
            <div class="charts-note">
              <h3>Size Chart Notes</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>All measurements are in inches.</li>
                <li>Custom sizes are available upon request.</li>
                <li>Rectangular patches are measured width x height.</li>
                <li>For irregular shapes, we measure the widest points.</li>
                <li>Pricing varies based on size and complexity.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
