              <p>Computer screens can display colors slightly differently from real thread or fabric. If there is a color issue, our sales team will contact you with alternate options.</p>
              <p>You can also visit <a href="https://www.pantone.com/pantone-connect" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pantone Connect</a> to verify official color references before production.</p>
            </div>
